trans-unit.source: Provides the URL from which a code assembly originates as evidence for policy evaluation.
trans-unit.target: Gir URL-adressen som en kode samling stammer fra som bevis for policyevaluering.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The presence of Url evidence produces a <xref:System.Security.Permissions.UrlIdentityPermission> in the grant set.
trans-unit.target: Finnes bevis for URL-adressen produserer en <xref:System.Security.Permissions.UrlIdentityPermission>i tildelingen.</xref:System.Security.Permissions.UrlIdentityPermission>

trans-unit.source: If there is a <xref:System.Security.CodeAccessPermission.Demand%2A> for <xref:System.Security.Permissions.UrlIdentityPermission>, the <xref:System.Security.Permissions.UrlIdentityPermission> that corresponds to the Url evidence is compared to the demanded permission.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er en <xref:System.Security.CodeAccessPermission.Demand%2A>for <xref:System.Security.Permissions.UrlIdentityPermission>, <xref:System.Security.Permissions.UrlIdentityPermission>som tilsvarer URL-adressen bevis sammenlignet med den nødvendige tillatelsen.</xref:System.Security.Permissions.UrlIdentityPermission> </xref:System.Security.Permissions.UrlIdentityPermission> </xref:System.Security.CodeAccessPermission.Demand%2A>

trans-unit.source: The complete URL is considered, including the protocol (HTTP, HTTPS, FTP) and the file.
trans-unit.target: Fullstendig URL-adressen anses, inkludert protokollen (HTTP, HTTPS, FTP) og filen.

trans-unit.source: For example, http://www.fourthcoffee.com/process/grind.htm is a complete URL.
trans-unit.target: Http://www.fourthcoffee.com/process/grind.htm er for eksempel en fullstendig URL-adresse.

trans-unit.source: URLs can be matched exactly or by a wildcard in the final position.
trans-unit.target: URL-adresser kan samsvare nøyaktig eller av jokertegn i endelig plasseringen.

trans-unit.source: For example, http://www.fourthcoffee.com/process/* is a wildcard URL.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel er http://www.fourthcoffee.com/process/ * en URL-adresse for jokertegn.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Policy.Url"></xref> class with the URL from which a code assembly originates.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Policy.Url"> </xref> klasse URL-adressen som en kode samling stammer fra.

trans-unit.source: The URL of origin for the associated code assembly.
trans-unit.target: URL-adressen innstilling for den tilknyttede code-samlingen.
